        "subject": "LU-7848 target: Do not fail MDT-MDT connection",
        "message": "LU-7848 target: Do not fail MDT-MDT connection\n\nWhen one MDT restarts, and try to connect to another\nMDT with the new cookie, let's do not fail it, otherwise\nit might cause eviction between MDT.\n\nSigned-off-by: Di Wang <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I63ec7f591679d63fbb1dbd54769225194e12e5e1\n"
